Ini bukan whitepaper crypto, tapi digital treasury prospectus
Cocok untuk:
•	Board of Directors
•	Institutional partners
•	Auditors
•	Regulators
API : Prospectus Summary
GET /api/prospectus/summary
{
  "entity": "PT Bitcoin Treasury Global",
  "treasuryObjective": "Preserve capital & hedge inflation",
  "assetPolicy": {
    "btcAllocationTarget": "60–75%",
    "rebalancePolicy": "Annual review"
  },
  "custody": "Institutional multi-signature cold storage",
  "riskDisclosure": [
    "Market volatility",
    "Regulatory uncertainty",
    "Technology risk"
  ]
}


app/api/prospectus/summary/route.ts
export async function GET() {
  return Response.json({
    entity: "PT Bitcoin Treasury Global",
    treasuryObjective: "Preserve capital & hedge inflation",
    assetPolicy: {
      btcAllocationTarget: "60–75%",
      rebalancePolicy: "Annual review"
    },
    custody: "Institutional multi-signature cold storage",
    riskDisclosure: [
      "Market volatility",
      "Regulatory uncertainty",
      "Technology risk"
    ]
  });
}
API : Prospectus performance disclosure
GET /api/prospectus/performance
{
  "historicalPerformance": {
    "btcCAGR": "42%",
    "fiatInflationAvg": "6.2%",
    "relativeOutperformance": "+35%"
  },
  "stressScenarios": [
    "BTC -50% → Treasury impact -32%",
    "BTC +100% → Treasury impact +68%"
  ]
}
